CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 29, 1958, pg. B26, reads: "This is the Way! - Teen-age dancers Hope Tucker and Willa Fountaine are shown teaching routines to younger dancers in their capacities as dance instructors at Howe Studios, East Liberty... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Dancer Willa Fountaine wearing long-sleeved leotard with collar and zipper, posed in Howe Studios, East Liberty
